reviews.review_text:
Excellent Aud Remarkable bass response. a well-played outing.

you shall love every note.

Another great show from a great tour Fall 1984 remains my favorite tour. Besides an unusaul pre drums setlist, the second set features a nice (if undeveloped) "Caution" jam in the middle of "Just wanna' make love". Additionally, the space segment is unusually melodic and I'm sure someone out there could pick out the tune Jerry's hinting at.
Best Audience version I like the sound of this version best.
